title: Akanga — Phase Progression

node: Phase 0 | id: p0 | type: card | pos: 550,60 | color: blue | body: Parser + Atomic Write\nNode / Edge models
node: Phase 1 | id: p1 | type: card | pos: 550,200 | color: blue | body: Edge schema + [[links]]\nWorkspace registry\nSync queue
node: Phase 2 | id: p2 | type: card | pos: 550,340 | color: teal | body: SQLite DB (WAL + FTS5)\nIndexer + Links module
node: Phase 3 | id: p3 | type: card | pos: 550,480 | color: teal | body: Graph algorithms\nBFS ego-graph traversal
node: Phase 4 | id: p4 | type: card | pos: 550,620 | color: orange | body: EventBus (pub/sub)\nVaultWatcher + Debouncer\nThread-async bridge
node: Phase 5 | id: p5 | type: card | pos: 300,760 | color: green | body: Terminal UI (Textual)\nSidebar + Markdown viewer
node: Phase 6 | id: p6 | type: card | pos: 550,760 | color: green | body: REST API (FastAPI)\nWebSocket real-time
node: Phase 7 | id: p7 | type: card | pos: 800,760 | color: green | body: Git integration\nAuto-commit on change
node: Phase 8 | id: p8 | type: card | pos: 550,900 | color: purple | body: MCP Server (FastMCP)\nRAG context builder\nClaude integration

